      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUMBUK WANG WANG (1) quickly away to win over the 460m at Warragul two runs back then prominent throughout when finishing third at Warragul last start. Key chance in this line up. CRACKERJACK LES (8) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot before finishing third (19.58) and beaten 1.5 lengths over 350m at this track. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expecting another good run. SONIC DIESEL (7) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 1.75 lengths (16.99) behind Idyllic James at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and six minor placings. Expected to be in the finish again. SAILAWAY GIN (2) has claims fresh from a recent placing in good time.",
